Package: ScalingFunctions
Type: Package
Title: Collection of functions for scaling of distributions
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Nikolai Knapp
Maintainer: Nikolai Knapp <nikolai.knapp@ufz.de>
Description: The package provides function for calculating parameters and moments of common 
probability distributions of environmental data. Further, there are functions
for transferring distributions accross scales, random sampling of arbitrary 
distributions and rank transformations.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
